Subject: [PATCH 1/1] Rename youtube-dl / youtube_dl references to youtube-dlc
 / youtube_dlc respectively.

---
 pafy/backend_internal.py   |  2 +-
 pafy/backend_youtube_dl.py |  8 ++++----
 pafy/jsinterp.py           |  4 ++--
 pafy/pafy.py               | 10 +++++-----
